<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Global Private Email Service</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        .gradient-bg {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="gradient-bg text-white font-sans min-h-screen">
    <nav class="max-w-7xl mx-auto p-6 flex justify-between items-center">
        <div class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tighter text-blue-400">
            CORE<span class="text-white">MAIL</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden md:flex space-x-8 text-sm font-medium text-slate-300">
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition">서비스 소개</a>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition">보안 기술</a>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition">API 문서</a>
        </div>
        <button class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 px-5 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-bold transition">
            로그인
        </button>
    </nav>

    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-24 text-center px-6">
        <header class="mb-12">
            <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 mb-6 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-blue-400 uppercase border border-blue-400 rounded-full">
                Next-Gen Email Infrastructure
            </span>
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 tracking-tight">
                당신만의 독자적인 <br><span class="text-blue-500">이메일 브랜드</span>를 구축하세요
            </h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                복잡한 서버 설정 없이, 안전하고 독립적인 이메일 통신망을 제공합니다. 
                지금 바로 원하는 주소를 선점하세요.
            </p>
        </header>
        
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-xl p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border border-slate-700/50 max-w-md mx-auto">
            <div class="flex flex-col space-y-4">
                <div class="relative">
                    <input type="text" placeholder="원하는 이메일 아이디" 
                           class="w-full bg-slate-900/80 border border-slate-700 p-4 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 transition text-lg">
                    <span class="absolute right-4 top-4 text-slate-500 font-medium">@is-a.dev</span>
                </div>
                <button class="bg-white text-slate-900 hover:bg-blue-500 hover:text-white transition py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg shadow-lg">
                    가입 가능 여부 확인
                </button>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-slate-500">
                * 현재 베타 테스트 기간으로 무료 등록이 가능합니다.
            </p>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="mt-32 pb-12 text-slate-600 text-sm text-center border-t border-slate-800 pt-8">
        <p>&copy; 2026 CoreMail Systems. Private & Secure Communication.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
